  factionOverview: Little is known of this faction. Their planet, which we call "Greenhouse-Mother",
    is overwhelmed by trillions of sentient plants that are connected by a communal
    nervous system. Their technology is primitive, but their zeal in spreading plantlife
    more than makes up for it.
